title: The probability of Fed hiking rates has gone down, says Invesco's Kristina Hooper
text:
The probability of Fed hiking rates has gone down, says Invesco's Kristina Hooper Wednesday, February 14, 2018 - 06:26 
If the Fed under new leadership of Jerome Powell is as data-dependent as the Yellen Fed, it's going to look for more data than just one jobs report, says Kristina Hooper, chief global market strategist at Invesco. Aleksandra Michalska reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
